cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or its companion papers, please cite it as below."
title: "maktaba-web-local — The Speaking Library (المكتبة الناطقة)"
abstract: >-
  A fully offline, on-device, privacy-preserving, multilingual (Arabic + English)
  personal digital library with retrieval-augmented question answering and a
  label-free, per-tenant self-calibrating relevance gate. This repository
  accompanies one flagship paper and three companion papers on multi-tenant
  sparse-retrieval starvation, continual cross-script glossary learning, and safe
  deterministic Iraqi-dialect rewriting.
type: software
authors:
